Jon Durr

I am a collaborative professional with about 4 years of diverse experience in implementation management and research. I became passionate about Software Engineering while working at Healthcare Bluebook and leading implementations for 10+ standard and enterprise clients. My biomedical engineering background makes me strong in problem solving, data analysis, and research. I'm currently open to opportunities as a Software Engineer for a company looking for a team member who is hungry to learn new technologies, provide value, and deliver results.
